WEBVTT

00:04:58.399 --> 00:05:00.297
Somebody who got educated here.

00:05:00.321 --> 00:05:02.995
Did they trust me? Of course not.

00:05:03.622 --> 00:05:07.936
So I really needed to build
the trust in this community.

00:05:07.960 --> 00:05:09.801
How am I going to do that?

00:05:10.372 --> 00:05:13.269
I went and surveyed and looked and looked.

00:05:13.626 --> 00:05:14.935
I asked.

00:05:14.959 --> 00:05:17.221
Finally, I found one man.

00:05:17.674 --> 00:05:19.110
He was 80 years old.

00:05:19.412 --> 00:05:20.824
He was a mullah.

00:05:21.435 --> 00:05:24.070
I went to his tent in the camp,

00:05:24.451 --> 00:05:26.046
and I asked him,

00:05:26.070 --> 00:05:28.165
"I want to make you a teacher."

00:05:29.117 --> 00:05:30.768
And he looked at me,